    EldaView.BasicView, EldaView.DescriptionView

    public class EldaView
extends CommonNodeWrapper
implements Comparable<EldaView>
    Encapsulates a view of an underlying Elda result set by specifying the properties that should be presented for the resources selected into the result set.
    Author:
    Ian Dickinson, Epimorphics (mailto:ian@epimorphics.com)
